 ext robin hood trail a short time later 
 now at street level backing down robin hood trail as lester runs toward us he carries a walkman and wears earphones and we hear the beatles singing back in the as he runs the endorphins have kicked in and lester grins reveling in the sheer physical pleasure of his body 
